Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我實現…我的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就像「黃泉歸來」裡的情節嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.00,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}黃泉歸來（黄泉がえり），梶尾真治的小說及同名電影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間為了讓你實現她的願望竟然會從黃泉歸來！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…我想那只是我所看見的幻想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想？你是說fantasy？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在這裡嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…現在不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！是我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪啊 芽間 露個臉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子一熱就把芽間的事情全盤托出了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他居然這麼老實地就接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:22.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽間～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我看不到她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都說是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳果然好厲害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個秘密基地是你在用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過只是我在日本停留的時候用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些紅色的 就是我去過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想看遍世界各地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是打工攢錢 然後去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那高中怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種地方 我沒空去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我去東南亞走了一轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越南的女人很可愛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前個子小小的 現在都長得熊一樣大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}像醬紫 醬紫～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真是可愛得不行了啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有變…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來「森林探險」不？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.64,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}會有什麼跑出來呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跑題了跑題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說芽間的心願吧 你們有過什麼約定不？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…她是不是說過想要仁碳你手裡那個「就是呀」的簽名？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:38.28,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}「就是呀（ですよ。）」，日本一搞笑藝人的藝名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會專門為了「就是撒」而變鬼跑出來嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…是那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 栗丸你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家後我會給你喝優酪乳的啦 優酪乳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子啊 你還真的去宿海家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得去找那家裡蹲真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是啊 偶爾不也會這樣嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 總覺得提不起勁 或是早上不想起床之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也會…不 經常會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦 不過我才不想和那種陰暗的傢伙相提並論呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在肯定在拿鳴子想一些色色的事情 一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 有可能～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人搞毛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王大附中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賤貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 你忘東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況你放在那不管就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被別人看到我跟綠高的人說話 那得有多難堪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好心給你拿過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒求你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:00.56,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}安鳴和鶴見子都是 別吵架啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候開始變得這麼自傲的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前可是一直都小心翼翼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是一點沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就一直容易被人影響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 跟一起來的那些大腿都已經合不攏的女人一個模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還虧你以前一直在模仿著本間芽衣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不許你隨便拿那死去的孩子的名字來說事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己說出來然後自己覺得痛苦 你還真是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 雪集也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想…變得跟芽間一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 仁碳你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡芽間…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是沒用那種話去挑明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…誰會喜歡這種醜八怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…也不會變成那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙叫了就要回家～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙叫了就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 要回到哪裡去才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想找什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？「奇妙寶貝」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.49,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}名字改自「神奇寶貝（ポケモン）」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還對客人要買的東西有意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要哪一代的啊？「蛋白石」還是「綠寶石」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「金」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？「奇妙寶貝·金」？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都多少年前的東西了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 有的話就賣給我！而且趕緊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？稀有奇妙寶貝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 芽間不是超想要的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說 她還真是提過「建築工」之類的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就肯定是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4571日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前出的遊戲 這定價也太暴利了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要說清楚了 這是良心價啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為基本已經買不到了 所以要賣貴點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了！多謝惠顧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我在工作室燒製成功了一個頗讚的盤子 所以晚飯吃烤肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊 一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼弄來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從最初的三隻裡面選一隻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壓力實體化形成的 我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是不應該存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.02,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(266,510)}第二集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(323,598)}勇者芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波…久川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前那樣叫我波波就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次有人用那種稱呼叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意啦 說起來雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間在仁碳那裡復活了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 到現在還…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海是怎麼說芽間的事情的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 仁碳 那麼久沒見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還是一如既往地強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海是怎麼說芽間的事情的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…幻聽？ 還是幻想來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間好像請他來實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 半路睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你怎麼去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸還沒出門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 總覺得洗澡的時候身上冷冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間最討厭那樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 也給我稍微注意一下自己的成長…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 某部分好像沒怎麼成長就是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先給我把衣服穿上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？好像是在哪裡見過的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 難道是波波君？好大塊頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}成長期真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友交換？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 聽說用數據線和朋友交換奇妙寶貝的話就能拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 肉太美味了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚剩下的而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叔叔就去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一魯粥…一路走好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 我都忘得一乾二淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 芽間也說過如果不是大家一起的話就實現不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強啊波波 你是怎麼想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢 我也看到幻聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻聽是看不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 只要再多弄到一個「奇妙寶貝」的遊戲軟體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再選一個不同的妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時最討厭自己的卷髮和眼鏡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對擁有光滑柔順長髮的芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被仁碳所喜歡的芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴 我們來貼配對的貼紙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這個很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也給安鳴一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很喜歡芽間 卻又很討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子 有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼嘛 我也要玩「奇妙寶貝」？這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾玩一下有什麼問題嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當尋找童真好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 眼鏡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵…吵死了 不戴又沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你們兩個也好久沒來過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚鳴子做的果凍要吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 安鳴的果凍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用那種稱呼叫我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 芽間的願望就是那個稀有奇妙寶貝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 別說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥 芽間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是她托夢給我…之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…「奇妙寶貝」…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 那裡是「LOVE AND PERRY」的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:39.11,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}惡搞世嘉卡片式遊戲「時尚魔女 LOVE AND BERRY」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是「猛牛王者」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.81,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}「猛牛王者」嗎 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}要找的不是「猛牛王者」 是「奇妙寶貝」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼從剛才開始 你一直都不過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 有芽間在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和安鳴都會很難過的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:53.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}「呆呆妖怪」也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:54.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你說「呆呆妖怪」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:55.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那和電視裡放的也有點不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:56.74,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.34,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}但是我們要找的是「奇妙寶貝」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}對了 「奇妙寶貝」「奇妙寶貝」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你到底有沒在找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:04.39,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}當然有了 你才是有沒好好地找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}肯定在找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 「BO☆BO-BO」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.83,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(181,188)}安城鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.83,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(160,153)}名字：
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種小小的遊戲軟體還要貼個名字 你還真是一絲不苟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒看「BO☆BO-BO」了 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以置信 為啥沒有泡伊特怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀有奇妙寶貝不是要用泡伊山怪和袋鼠怪去交換嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野外是沒有泡伊山怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用泡伊特進化才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 安鳴還是沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很溫柔 有很多漫畫和遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是和那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情景…總覺得好久沒見過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 泡伊山怪出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也沒什麼啦 消磨時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了你的報酬 有麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要錢的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來學校…上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要連上數據線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這就可以和朋友進行交換了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 稍等
